<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:13:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>路透调查显示，普遍预计中国8月份将维持贷款基准LPR不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widely-expected-keep-lending-benchmark-lprs-unchanged-aug-2024-08-19/</link><description>路透社的一项调查显示，中国政策制定者在 7 月份下调了一系列关键利率，令全球市场感到意外，预计中国周二将维持基准贷款利率不变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 19:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widely-expected-keep-lending-benchmark-lprs-unchanged-aug-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>资金撤退，实物买家赢得铜市争夺战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/physical-buyers-win-battle-copper-market-funds-retreat-2024-08-19/</link><description>逃离铜市场的投资者可能会在数月内处于观望状态，这为预计主要消费国中国和其他地区的需求在未来几个月内恶化并对价格造成压力的实体参与者留下了空间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/physical-buyers-win-battle-copper-market-funds-retreat-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：杰克逊霍尔迫在眉睫，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-19/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯猪肉生产商瞄准欧盟在中国猪肉市场的份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russian-pork-producers-target-eus-share-chinas-pork-market-2024-08-19/</link><description>俄罗斯猪肉生产商的目标是在未来几年内占据中国猪肉进口市场10%的份额，寻求利用欧盟与全球最大猪肉消费国中国之间的贸易紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:18:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russian-pork-producers-target-eus-share-chinas-pork-market-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>德国军舰等待穿越台湾海峡的命令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/german-warships-await-orders-crossing-disputed-taiwan-strait-2024-08-19/</link><description>两艘德国军舰的指挥官表示，两艘德国军舰正在等待柏林的命令，以确定下个月它们是否将成为数十年来第一批穿过台湾海峡的德国海军舰艇，此举遭到了北京的谴责。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/german-warships-await-orders-crossing-disputed-taiwan-strait-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>奥运选手在网上辱骂后，中国针对“混乱”的粉丝群体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-takes-aim-chaotic-fan-groups-after-olympians-abused-online-2024-08-19/</link><description>中国政府和官方体育机构谴责球迷利用社交媒体攻击和散布有关中国奥运选手的谣言，并表示这种行为对运动员、教练及其家人造成了极其负面的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 05:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-takes-aim-chaotic-fan-groups-after-olympians-abused-online-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>领导人会晤后，中国和越南签署了从铁路到鳄鱼的14项协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnams-top-leaders-meet-beijing-2024-08-19/</link><description>周一，中国国家主席习近平在北京会见越南新任领导人苏林后，中国和越南签署了涵盖跨境铁路和鳄鱼出口等领域的 14 份文件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 03:44:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnams-top-leaders-meet-beijing-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国启动针对朝鲜军事和网络威胁的年度演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-kick-off-annual-drills-over-norths-military-cyber-threats-2024-08-19/</link><description>韩国和美国周一开始了一年一度的夏季军事演习，旨在加强两国抵御朝鲜武器和网络威胁的联合准备。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-kick-off-annual-drills-over-norths-military-cyber-threats-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>原中国足协副主席因受贿被判有期徒刑11年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/former-chinese-football-vice-president-gets-11-years-jail-bribery-2024-08-19/</link><description>据国家通讯社新华社周一援引法院裁决称，中国足协前副主席因受贿罪被判处 11 年有期徒刑，并处罚金 100 万元人民币（139,579.03 美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 01:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/former-chinese-football-vice-president-gets-11-years-jail-bribery-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙停火谈判和中国经济疲软，油价每桶下跌逾 2 美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-china-demand-fears-focus-mideast-talks-2024-08-19/</link><description>由于中东和平谈判的成功前景将降低供应风险，周一油价每桶下跌逾 2 美元，而主要石油进口国中国的经济疲软可能会抑制需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 01:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-china-demand-fears-focus-mideast-talks-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>美联储消息公布前，华尔街股市上涨，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-19/</link><description>由于预期美国经济将避免衰退且通胀降温将刺激降息，上周股市飙升，全球股市周一走高，美元走低。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>南海船只相撞后，菲律宾与中国相互指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-deliberately-collided-with-chinese-vessel-south-2024-08-19/</link><description>菲律宾和中国周一互相指责对方在南海撞船并进行危险的演习，这是两国上个月同意试图解决海上分歧后的最新冲突。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-deliberately-collided-with-chinese-vessel-south-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>越南最高领导人苏林抵达中国会见习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-top-leader-lam-arrives-china-set-meet-xi-jinping-2024-08-18/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，越南最高领导人苏林周日抵达中国进行为期三天的访问，北京外交部表示，访问期间将包括与国家主席习近平和国务院总理李强的会面。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-top-leader-lam-arrives-china-set-meet-xi-jinping-2024-08-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国在暂停后发布新的黄金进口配额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-issues-new-gold-import-quotas-after-pause-sources-2024-08-16/</link><description>四位知情人士告诉路透社，尽管金价创历史新高，但中国几家银行已获得央行新的黄金进口配额，预计需求将会复苏。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-issues-new-gold-import-quotas-after-pause-sources-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>李克强：中国将着力促进消费提振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-focus-boosting-consumption-improve-economy-premier-says-2024-08-16/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国总理李强周五在内阁全体会议上表示，必须大力提振经济，国家将把重点放在刺激消费上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-focus-boosting-consumption-improve-economy-premier-says-2024-08-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>